%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22I've%20lived%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Brazil%20for%20the%20last%2024%20years.%20Moving%20with%20little%20kids%20is%20very%20different%20than%20with%20teens.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221863%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Andrew%20Jernigan%20and%20his%20family%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674671dffa0140cdd565bfac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221397%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAndrew%20Jernigan%20and%20his%20family%20moved%20between%20Brazil%20and%20the%20US%20multiple%20times.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Andrew%20Jernigan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAndrew%20Jernigan%2C%2051%2C%20has%20moved%20with%20his%20family%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Brazil%20multiple%20times.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20last%20time%20he%20lived%20in%20Brazil%2C%20his%20children%20were%20teenagers%20and%20found%20the%20move%20difficult.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20says%20that%20when%20moving%20with%20kids%20older%20than%2012%2C%20parents%20need%20to%20think%20about%20safety%20and%20college.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Andrew%20Jernigan%2C%20CEO%20of%20Insured%20Nomads.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20time%20I%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrazil-to-us-midwest-moving-culture-shocks-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emoved%20to%20Brazil%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20in%202000%20to%20marry%20a%20Brazilian%20woman%20I%20had%20been%20introduced%20to%20by%20a%20friend%20and%20had%20been%20writing%20to%20for%20quite%20some%20time.%20We%20were%20engaged%20on%20my%20first%20visit%20and%20married%20the%20following%20year%20after%20I%20moved%20there.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20family%20%3Cspan%3Ehas%20moved%20four%20times%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Brazil.%20We%20learned%20that%20there%20are%20more%20things%20to%20consider%20when%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraveling-with-teens-easier-than-traveling-little-kids-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emoving%20with%20teenagers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Ethan%20when%20moving%20with%20little%20kids.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2230a94da6-792d-4697-abf9-cae974b83f08%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20moved%20to%20Brazil%2C%20so%20our%20kids%20could%20connect%20with%20their%20mom's%20culture%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20getting%20married%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20moved%20back%20to%20the%20US%20and%20then%20to%20Ghana%20for%20a%20time%20for%20her%20work.%20In%202008%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20take%20some%20time%20to%20live%20back%20in%20Brazil%20with%20our%20three%20young%20children.%20We%20wanted%20our%20children%2C%20who%20were%20half%20Brazilian%2C%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftravel%2Fbabbel-language-learning-overview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elearn%20Portuguese%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20be%20exposed%20to%20different%20cultures.%20We%20also%20wanted%20to%20live%20somewhere%20for%20a%20while%20with%20a%20low%20cost%20of%20living%20to%20enjoy%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20dollar's%20value.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20moved%20back%20to%20the%20US%20when%20I%20had%20a%20job%20opportunity%20in%20Northern%20California.%20It%20was%20an%20adventure%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-worst-things-about-leaving-san-francisco-for-la-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efun%20times%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20hiking%20in%20the%20mountains%2C%20and%20a%20community%20of%20diverse%20nationalities%20that%20the%20kids%20thrived%20in%20as%20well.%20My%20wife%20pursued%20further%20education%20while%20there%2C%20then%20her%20MBA%20and%20MPH%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Alabama.%20A%20company%20in%20Brazil%20hired%20her%2C%20so%20we%20made%20another%20move%20to%20Brazil%20in%202019.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20we%20lived%20in%20Brazil%20without%20children%20or%20with%20young%20children%2C%20there%20was%20nothing%20but%20good%20about%20living%20abroad.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-affordable-places-to-live-in-america-lowest-cost-living-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecost%20of%20living%20was%20cheaper%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20the%20children%20could%20attend%20local%20schools%2C%20pick%20up%20the%20language%2C%20and%20experience%20Brazilian%20culture.%20As%20a%20family%2C%20we'd%20escape%20to%20the%20mountains%20and%20seaside%20for%20days%20out.%20We%20felt%20that%20we%20could%20have%20lived%20there%20forever.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20last%20stint%20of%20living%20in%20Brazil%2C%20from%202019%20to%202021%2C%20our%20children%20were%20all%20over%20the%20age%20of%2012%2C%20and%20we%20had%20to%20consider%20their%20futures%20and%20their%20safety.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2282a29852-b3db-4577-b75b-5fbbff7aa9a8%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20had%20to%20budget%20for%20private%20schools%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20kids%20wanted%20the%20opportunity%20to%20attend%20universities%20outside%20Brazil.%20This%20meant%20that%20we%20couldn't%20put%20them%20in%20the%20local%20Brazilian%20schools%20because%20they%20wouldn't%20allow%20them%20to%20work%20toward%20SATs%20or%20A-levels%20to%20get%20into%20American%20or%20British%20universities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInstead%2C%20we%20budgeted%20to%20place%20them%20in%20the%20American%20School%20of%20Rio%20de%20Janeiro.%20They%20got%20a%20great%20education%20and%20were%20exposed%20to%20expats%20from%20all%20around%20the%20world%2C%20but%20it%20was%20very%20expensive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20school%20didn't%20have%20the%20same%20level%20of%20sports%20clubs%20as%20in%20the%20US.%20My%20daughter%20had%20played%20lacrosse%2C%20and%20my%20son%20wanted%20to%20row%20for%20the%20crew%20%E2%80%94%20neither%20of%20those%20sports%20was%20available%20to%20them%20in%20Brazil.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22255af7c8-dfe8-4bde-bbed-87cc96dc2083%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20moved%20back%20to%20the%20US%20for%20many%20reasons%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20teenagers%2C%20they%20wanted%20to%20be%20independent%20of%20us%2C%20but%20we%20had%20to%20be%20very%20watchful%20of%20them%20due%20to%20safety%20concerns.%20They%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-was-held-at-gunpoint-at-12-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecould%20be%20targets%20of%20theft%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20even%20kidnapping.%20We%20know%20it%20happens%2C%20and%20were%20very%20protective%20of%20them%20going%20around%20the%20city%20on%20their%20own.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhereas%20in%20the%20US%2C%20we%20wouldn't%20think%20twice%20about%20leaving%20them%20at%20parties%20or%20going%20to%20a%20friend's%20house%2C%20we%20were%20always%20on%20alert%20for%20their%20whereabouts%20and%20who%20they%20were%20with%20if%20they%20were%20out%20of%20the%20house%20while%20we%20were%20in%20Brazil.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20were%20little%20things%20they%20missed%2C%20too.%20They%20missed%20comfort%20foods%20like%20peanut%20butter%20and%20American%20candy.%20And%20we%20all%20missed%20our%20extended%20family.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20main%20reason%20we%20came%20back%20to%20the%20US%20in%202021%20was%20my%20kids'%20trajectory%20in%20school.%20Reintegrating%20back%20into%20American%20schools%20as%20teenagers%20had%20its%20challenges.%20Their%20friends%20had%20been%20in%20school%20together%2C%20going%20to%20birthday%20parties%20together%2C%20and%20attending%20summer%20camps%20together%20for%20three%20years.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20kids%20had%20missed%20all%20of%20it%20and%20had%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20insert%20themselves%20back%20into%20their%20old%20world.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2257df89ca-2918-48f0-98de-f743c8c92493%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20miss%20life%20in%20Brazil%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20though%20we%20knew%20moving%20back%20to%20the%20US%20was%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do%20while%20our%20children%20were%20still%20teens%2C%20we%20still%20remember%20the%20incredible%20beaches%2C%20forests%2C%20and%20mountains%20of%20Brazil.%20We%20all%20miss%20being%20able%20to%20quickly%20access%20the%20rugged%2C%20wild%20outdoors.%20There%20were%20always%20cultural%20activities%20we%20could%20go%20to%20as%20a%20family%2C%20and%20we%20spent%20hours%20eating%20together%20at%20restaurants%20with%20some%20of%20the%20best%20food%20I've%20ever%20tasted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20though%20we%20haven't%20ruled%20out%20living%20in%20Brazil%20in%20the%20future%2C%20we'll%20wait%20to%20move%20back%20until%20our%20kids%20are%20out%20of%20the%20house.%20But%20we'll%20be%20sure%20to%20visit%20often%20until%20we%20return%20to%20live%20again.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-has-moved-between-the-us-and-brazil-multiple-times-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735405981000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674671dffa0140cdd565bfac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-has-moved-between-the-us-and-brazil-multiple-times-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Andrew%20Jernigan's%20family%20has%20lived%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Brazil.%20He%20says%20that%20international%20moves%20are%20easier%20with%20little%20kids%20than%20with%20teenagers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Lauren%20Crosby%20Medlicott)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-has-moved-between-the-us-and-brazil-multiple-times-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Congress%20Attacks%20Over%20Manmohan%20Singh%20Funeral%2C%20JP%20Nadda's%20'Super%20PM'%20Swipe%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20escalation%20of%20the%20row%20over%20the%20choice%20of%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh's%20cremation%20site%2C%20senior%20Congress%20leaders%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20attacked%20the%20BJP-ruled%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20accused%20it%20of%20%26quot%3Binsulting%26quot%3B%20the%20memory%20of%20the%20two-term%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20not%20thinking%20beyond%20%26quot%3Bpolitics%20and%20narrow-mindedness%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeading%20a%20no-holds-barred%20counterattack%2C%20BJP%20president%20JP%20Nadda%20said%20the%20Congress%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20were%20playing%20%26quot%3Bcheap%20politics%26quot%3B%20in%20Mr%20Singh's%20name%20and%20accused%20the%20party%20of%20not%20doing%20justice%20to%20any%20leader%20who%20was%20not%20from%20the%20Nehru-Gandhi%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Singh%2C%20who%20died%20at%20the%20age%20of%2092%20on%20Thursday%2C%20was%20cremated%20at%20the%20Nigambodh%20Ghat%20in%20Delhi%20with%20full%20state%20honours%20on%20Saturday.%20A%20day%20before%20the%20funeral%2C%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20had%20written%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%2C%20citing%20Dr%20Singh's%20stature%20and%20his%20contributions%20to%20the%20country%2C%20requested%20that%20the%20last%20rites%20be%20conducted%20in%20a%20place%20where%20a%20memorial%20could%20also%20be%20built%20in%20his%20name.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20controversy%20over%20the%20memorial%20gathered%20steam%2C%20the%20Centre%20issued%20a%20release%20ahead%20of%20the%20funeral%20stating%20that%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20had%20said%20a%20place%20would%20be%20allocated%20for%20Dr%20Singh's%20memorial%20and%20the%20cremation%20should%20take%20place%20in%20the%20meantime.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Should%20Have%20Shown%20Respect'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20tweeted%20after%20the%20funeral%2C%20however%2C%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20%26quot%3Btotally%20insulted%26quot%3B%20the%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20from%20the%20Sikh%20community%20by%20having%20his%20last%20rites%20conducted%20at%20Nigambodh%20Ghat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20great%20son%20of%20Mother%20India%20and%20the%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20the%20Sikh%20community%2C%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%20ji%20has%20been%20totally%20insulted%20by%20the%20present%20government%20by%20performing%20his%20last%20rites%20today%20at%20the%20Nigambodh%20Ghat.%20He%20was%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%20for%20a%20decade%2C%20during%20his%20tenure%20the%20country%20became%20an%20economic%20superpower%20and%20his%20policies%20still%20support%20the%20poor%20and%20backward%20classes%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20is%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTill%20date%2C%20respecting%20the%20dignity%20of%20all%20former%20Prime%20Ministers%2C%20their%20last%20rites%20were%20performed%20at%20authorised%20burial%20sites%20so%20that%20every%20person%20could%20have%20the%20last%20%3Cem%3E'darshan'%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20pay%20homage%20without%20any%20inconvenience.%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%20deserves%20our%20highest%20respect%20and%20a%20memorial.%20The%20government%20should%20have%20shown%20respect%20to%20this%20great%20son%20of%20the%20country%20and%20his%20proud%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20many%20of%20the%20same%20issues%20as%20her%20brother%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20said%20the%20government%20should%20have%20thought%20%26quot%3Bbeyond%20politics%20and%20narrow-mindedness%26quot%3B%20when%20it%20came%20to%20Dr%20Singh's%20funeral%20site.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20not%20providing%20an%20adequate%20place%20for%20the%20cremation%20of%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20the%20Government%20has%20not%20done%20justice%20to%20the%20dignity%20of%20the%20post%20of%20former%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20the%20personality%20of%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20his%20legacy%20and%20the%20self-respecting%20Sikh%20community.%20Earlier%2C%20all%20former%20Prime%20Ministers%20were%20given%20the%20highest%20honour%20and%20respect.%20Dr.%20Manmohan%20Singh%20Ji%20deserves%20this%20honour%20and%20Samadhi%20Sthal...%20The%20government%20should%20have%20thought%20beyond%20politics%20and%20narrow-mindedness%20in%20this%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20MP%20also%20claimed%20that%20Dr%20Singh's%20family%20was%20%26quot%3Bstruggling%20for%20space%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20funeral%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Cheap%20Politics'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20the%20Congress%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20over%20the%20claims%2C%20BJP%20President%20JP%20Nadda%20said%20%26quot%3Bcheap%20politics%26quot%3B%20was%20being%20played%20over%20Dr%20Singh's%20cremation%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20Centre%20had%20already%20stated%20that%20space%20would%20be%20allotted%20for%20his%20memorial.%20Repeating%20a%20charge%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20frequently%20levelled%20against%20the%20Congress%2C%20he%20also%20accused%20the%20party%20of%20placing%20its%20then-president%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20as%20'super%20PM'%20over%20Manmohan%20Singh%20when%20he%20was%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20between%202004%20and%202014.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20indeed%20ironic%20that%20former%20Congress%20president%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20current%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20are%20not%20refraining%20from%20doing%20politics%20even%20over%20the%20sad%20demise%20of%20the%20country's%20former%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20the%20honourable%20Manmohan%20Singh...%20The%20Congress%2C%20which%20never%20gave%20real%20respect%20to%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%20while%20he%20was%20alive%2C%20is%20now%20doing%20politics%20in%20the%20name%20of%20his%20respect.%20This%20is%20the%20same%20Congress%20which%20tarnished%20the%20dignity%20of%20the%20PM%20post%20by%20placing%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20as%20'super%20PM'%20over%20PM%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20Minister%20said%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20swipe%20at%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20for%20%26quot%3Btearing%20up%26quot%3B%20an%20ordinance%20passed%20by%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20cabinet%20in%202013%2C%20the%20BJP%20politician%20also%20accused%20the%20Gandhis%20of%20neither%20respecting%20nor%20doing%20justice%20to%20any%20senior%20leader%20who%20was%20not%20from%20their%20family.%20He%20cited%20the%20examples%20of%20Sardar%20Patel%2C%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri%2C%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%2C%20Pranab%20Mukherjee%20and%20PV%20Narasimha%20Rao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20death%20of%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Shri%20Narasimha%20Rao%20on%2023%20December%2C%202004%2C%20there%20was%20a%20demand%20to%20build%20a%20%3Cem%3E'samadhi%20sthal'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(memorial)%20in%20Delhi's%20Rajghat%20complex%2C%20but%20super%20PM%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20did%20not%20approve%20it.%20His%20body%20was%20not%20even%20given%20a%20place%20in%20the%20Congress%20office.%20Congress%20did%20not%20want%20Narasimha%20Rao%20ji's%20last%20rites%20to%20be%20performed%20in%20Delhi%20and%20later%20his%20last%20rites%20were%20performed%20in%20Hyderabad.%20It%20was%20Prime%20Minister%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%20ji%20who%20also%20built%20a%20%3Cem%3E'samadhi'%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20Narasimha%20Rao%20ji%20in%202015%20and%20honoured%20him%20by%20giving%20him%20Bharat%20Ratna%20in%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20an%20estimate%2C%20Congress%20governments%20in%20the%20country%20have%20named%20about%20600%20government%20schemes%2C%20educational%20institutions%2C%20awards%2C%20roads%2C%20national%20parks%2C%20museums%2C%20airports%2C%20ports%2C%20buildings%20and%20sports%20after%20the%20Nehru-Gandhi%20family%2C%20while%20the%20number%20of%20schemes%20named%20after%20other%20personalities%20is%20very%20few.%20Our%20country%20will%20never%20forget%20and%20will%20never%20forgive%20the%20historical%20sins%20of%20the%20unprincipled%20Congress.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20other%20leaders%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20should%20refrain%20from%20such%20cheap%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735404960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fkn3n6vbg_rahul-gandhi-jp-nadda_625x300_28_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanmohan-singh-manmohan-singh-last-rites-on-congress-attacks-over-manmohan-singh-funeral-jp-naddas-super-pm-swipe-7352519%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20significant%20escalation%20of%20the%20row%20over%20the%20choice%20of%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh's%20cremation%20site%2C%20senior%20Congress%20leaders%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20attacked%20the%20BJP-ruled%20government%20at%20the%20Centre.%20BJP%20chief%20JP%20Nadda%20hit%20back.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Scorched%20beyond%20recognition'%20NYC%20subway%20horror%20victim%20still%20unidentified.%20What's%20next%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735404728000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116748316%2Cimgsize-1169157.cms%22%2C%2