akistan%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20the%20attacks%20in%20Afghanistan%20were%20organised...%20were%20targeted%20in%20retaliation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20provincial%20official%20in%20Khost%20told%20AFP%20the%20clashes%20forced%20residents%20to%20flee%20border%20areas%2C%20but%20that%20there%20were%20no%20reports%20of%20casualties%20among%20Afghan%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Khost%20city%2C%20the%20provincial%20capital%2C%20hundreds%20of%20Afghans%20demonstrated%20against%20Pakistan%20on%20Saturday%2C%20calling%20for%20accountability%20for%20civilian%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtester%20Najibullah%20Zaland%20said%20they%20demanded%20global%20economic%20pressure%20on%20Pakistan%20to%20prevent%20such%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20gathered%20here%20today%20to%20raise%20our%20voices%20to%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20path%20to%20peace%20must%20be%20put%20in%20place%2C%20or%20else%20the%20youth%20will%20not%20stay%20silent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20demonstrators%20praised%20the%20Afghan%20forces%2C%20with%20one%20protester%2C%20Rashidullah%20Hamdard%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3Bour%20fighters%20gave%20them%20a%20strong%20response%2C%20and%20we%20stand%20with%20our%20forces%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20demand%20the%20world%20hold%20the%20Pakistani%20military%20accountable%20for%20these%20cruel%20and%20foolish%20attacks%2C%26quot%3B%20Hamdard%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'Red%20line'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strikes%20were%20the%20latest%20spike%20in%20hostilities%20on%20the%20frontier%20between%20Afghanistan%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20with%20border%20tensions%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20escalating%20since%20the%20Taliban%20seized%20power%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIslamabad%20has%20accused%20Kabul's%20authorities%20of%20harbouring%20militant%20fighters%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20strike%20on%20Pakistani%20soil%20with%20impunity%20--%20allegations%20the%20Taliban%20government%20denies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESkirmishes%20along%20the%20frontier%20escalated%20after%20Pakistan's%20military%20conducted%20deadly%20air%20strikes%20in%20Afghanistan's%20border%20regions%20in%20March%2C%20which%20Taliban%20authorities%20claimed%20killed%20eight%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20assistance%20mission%20in%20Afghanistan%2C%20UNAMA%2C%20called%20for%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20%26quot%3Bcredible%20reports%26quot%3B%20of%20civilian%20deaths%2C%20as%20the%20UN%20children's%20agency%20UNICEF%20said%20%26quot%3Bchildren%20are%20not%20and%20must%20never%20be%20a%20target%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUNICEF%20is%20deeply%20saddened%20by%20reports%20that%20at%20least%2020%20children%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20an%20attack%20near%20the%20border%20in%20eastern%20Afghanistan%2C%26quot%3B%20regional%20director%20Sanjay%20Wijesekera%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20comes%20after%20the%20Tehreek-e-Taliban%20Pakistan%20(TTP)%20--%20who%20share%20a%20common%20ideology%20with%20their%20Afghan%20counterparts%20--%20last%20week%20claimed%20a%20raid%20on%20an%20army%20outpost%20near%20the%20border%20with%20Afghanistan%2C%20which%20Pakistan%20said%20killed%2016%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20desire%20good%20ties%20with%20them%20(Kabul)%20but%20TTP%20should%20be%20stopped%20from%20killing%20our%20innocent%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Pakistan's%20Prime%20Minister%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20said%20in%20a%20cabinet%20address%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20our%20red%20line%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20has%20been%20battling%20a%20resurgence%20of%20militant%20violence%20in%20its%20western%20border%20regions%20since%20the%20Taliban's%20takeover%20in%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202024%20alone%2C%20the%20military%20has%20reported%20383%20soldiers%20and%20925%20militants%20killed%20in%20various%20clashes.%3C%2Fp%3