F676e83ee9de00e389eb38ae2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221984%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20crash%20site%20of%20the%20plane.%3Cp%3EMeiramgul%20Kussainova%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERussian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20has%20apologized%20to%20Azerbaijan%20for%20the%20fatal%20Azerbaijan%20Airlines%20plane%20crash.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPutin%20did%20not%20take%20responsibility%2C%20however.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExperts%20and%20the%20White%20House%20say%20there%20is%20evidence%20the%20plane%20may%20have%20been%20hit%20by%20Russian%20air%20defenses.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERussian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20has%20apologized%20to%20the%20president%20of%20Azerbaijan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairlines-avoid-russia-airspace-after-azerbaijan-airlines-crash-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efor%20the%20recent%20fatal%20Azerbaijan%20Airlines%20plane%20crash%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20he%20stopped%20short%20of%20claiming%20responsibility%20for%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Kremlin%20said%20on%20Saturday%20that%20Putin%20apologized%20during%20a%20phone%20call%20with%20Azerbaijan's%20president%2C%20Ilham%20Aliyev.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Kremlin's%20press%20office%20said%20that%20Putin%20had%20%26quot%3Boffered%20his%20apologies%20that%20the%20tragic%20incident%20had%20occurred%20in%20Russia's%20airspace%20and%20once%20again%20conveyed%20his%20deep%20and%20sincere%20condolences%20to%20the%20families%20of%20the%20plane%20crash%20victims%20and%20wished%20those%20injured%20the%20quickest%20recovery%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20Russia's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftass.com%2Fpolitics%2F1894845%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETass%20news%20agency%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAzerbaijan%20Airlines%20flight%20Flight%208243%20crash-landed%20in%20Kazakhstan%20on%20Wednesday.%20Kazakh%20authorities%20said%2038%20people%20died%2C%20including%20the%20pilots%2C