0Sona%20Mohapatra%20reflects%20on%20Aishwarya%20Rai's%20transformation%20from%20an%20articulate%2C%20confident%20woman%20to%20a%20more%20diplomatic%20public%20figure%2C%20suggesting%20industry%20pressure%20may%20be%20a%20factor.%20Sona%20also%20discusses%20her%20own%20work%20ethic%20of%20working%2018%20hours%20daily%20to%20maintain%20her%20independence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsona-mohapatra-describes-changes-she-has-seen-in-aishwarya-rai-before-and-after-she-won-miss-world-title-maybe-the-industry-compels-her-to-not-be-too-smart%2Farticleshow%2F116744280.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manmohan%20Singh%20Funeral%20Site%20An%20%26quot%3BInsult%26quot%3B%2C%20Says%20Rahul%20Gandhi%3B%20BJP%20Hits%20Back%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20row%20over%20the%20choice%20of%20site%20for%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh's%20cremation%20and%20a%20possible%20memorial%20in%20his%20name%20escalated%20today%20after%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20accused%20the%20Centre%20of%20%26quot%3Binsulting%26quot%3B%20the%20memory%20of%20the%20former%20prime%20minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Singh%2C%20who%20served%20as%20India's%20prime%20minister%20from%202004%20to%202014%2C%20died%20at%20the%20age%20of%2092%20on%20December%2026%20at%20AIIMS%20Delhi.%20His%20last%20rites%20were%20performed%20today%20at%20the%20Nigambodh%20Ghat%20with%20full%20state%20honours.%20The%20choice%20of%20the%20funeral%20site%20was%20flagged%20by%20Mr%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Binsult%26quot%3B%20to%20Dr%20Singh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20great%20son%20of%20Mother%20India%20and%20the%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20the%20Sikh%20community%2C%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%20ji%20has%20been%20totally%20insulted%20by%20the%20present%20government%20by%20performing%20his%20last%20rites%20today%20at%20the%20Nigambodh%20Ghat.%20He%20was%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%20for%20a%20decade%2C%20during%20his%20tenure%20the%20country%20became%20an%20economic%20superpower%20and%20his%20policies%20still%20support%20the%20poor%20and%20backward%20classes%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTill%20date%2C%20respecting%20the%20dignity%20of%20all%20former%20Prime%20Ministers%2C%20their%20last%20rites%20were%20performed%20at%20authorised%20burial%20sites%20so%20that%20every%20person%20could%20have%20the%20last%20'darshan'%20and%20pay%20homage%20without%20any%20inconvenience.%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%20deserves%20our%20highest%20respect%20and%20a%20memorial.%20The%20government%20should%20have%20shown%20respect%20to%20this%20great%20son%20of%20the%20country%20and%20his%20proud%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20was%20quick%20to%20rebuke%20the%20Congress%20for%20raising%20the%20issue%20on%20the%20day%20of%20Dr%20Singh's%20cremation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20spokesperson%20Sambit%20Patra%20criticised%20Mr%20Gandhi%20for%20his%20remarks%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20stooping%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bnew%20low%20in%20Indian%20politics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20new%20low%20in%20politics%20of%20India%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20Congress%20party.%20The%20kind%20of%20politics%20Congress%20is%20doing%2C%20especially%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20-%20who%20has%20tweeted%20about%20the%20cremation%20-%20is%20shameful.%20We%20in%20a%20cabinet%20meeting%20after%20the%20demise%20of%20the%20former%20PM%20Manmohan%20Singh%20-%20decided%20that%20since%20he%20was%20the%20PM%20and%20had%20a%20big%20stature%20%C2%A0-%20the%20cabinet%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20Congress%20and%20Dr%20Singh's%20family%20-%20where%20the%20cabinet%20said%20that%20we%20should%20build%20a%20memorial%20in%20his%20name%20so%20that%20the%20country%20and%20the%20world%20remember%20him%20for%20his%20positive%20works%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Patra%20said%20in%20a%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20further%20accused%20Congress%20of%20hypocrisy%2C%20pointing%20out%20past%20instances%20of%20alleged%20disrespect%20toward%20its%20own%20leaders%2C%20such%20as%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20PV%20Narasimha%20Rao%20and%20former%20President%20Pranab%20Mukherjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Singh's%20body%20was%20then%20taken%20to%20Nigambodh%20Ghat%20in%20a%20flower-adorned%20vehicle%2C%20accompanied%20by%20security%20personnel%20and%20a%20large%20gathering%20of%20supporters.%20Mr%20Gandhi%20walked%20alongside%20the%20procession%20and%20later%20helped%20carry%20the%20casket%20to%20the%20pyre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20cremation%20ground%2C%20the%20ceremony%20was%20attended%20by%20a%20host%20of%20dignitaries%2C%20including%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%2C%20Vice%20President%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%2C%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Leaders%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20such%20as%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20and%20Jairam%20Ramesh%2C%20were%20also%20present%2C%20along%20with%20senior%20BJP%20leaders%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20Rajnath%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20dignitaries%2C%20including%20Bhutanese%20King%20Jigme%20Khesar%20Namgyel%20Wangchuck%20and%20Mauritius%20Foreign%20Minister%20Dhananjay%20Ramful%2C%20joined%20the%20ceremony%20to%20honour%20Dr%20Singh's%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20prime%20minister's%20eldest%20daughter%2C%20Upinder%20Singh%2C%20lit%20the%20funeral%20pyre%2C%20as%20Sikh%20priests%20recited%20Gurbani%20hymns.%20The%20ceremony%20concluded%20with%20a%2021-gun%20salute%20by%20the%20armed%20forces.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735392180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fnlqhnn88_rahul-gandhi-ani-_625x300_28_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3