2C%20several%20members%20of%20the%20Royal%20family%20and%20senior%20officials%20of%20the%20Bhutanese%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20mark%20of%20respect%20to%20the%20late%20former%20prime%20minister%20and%20in%20solidarity%20with%20the%20government%20and%20people%20of%20India%2C%20all%20national%20flags%20across%20the%20country%20and%20at%20Bhutan's%20embassies%2C%20missions%2C%20and%20consulates%20abroad%20are%20being%20flown%20at%20half-mast%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Bhutanese%20government%20said%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20King%20Wangchuck%20paid%20rich%20tributes%20to%20Dr%20Singh%20at%20his%20funeral%20at%20the%20Nigambodh%20Ghat%20public%20cremation%20ground%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Singh%2C%20who%20served%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%20from%202004%20to%202014%20and%20widely%20known%20as%20the%20architect%20of%20India's%20economic%20reforms%2C%20died%20on%20Thursday%20night%20at%20the%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20(AIIMS).%20He%20was%2092.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20relations%20with%20several%20key%20countries%20including%20Bhutan%20saw%20significant%20upswing%20during%20Dr%20Singh's%20prime%20ministership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Bhutan%20enjoy%20strong%20bonds%20of%20friendship%20based%20on%20goodwill%2C%20trust%20and%20mutually%20beneficial%20cooperation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20basic%20framework%20of%20India-Bhutan%20relations%20is%20the%20'Treaty%20of%20Friendship%20and%20Cooperation'%20signed%20in%201949.%20It%20was%20renewed%20in%20February%202007%20when%20Dr%20Singh%20was%20the%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cooperation%20in%20the%20hydro-power%20sector%20is%20one%20of%20the%20cornerstones%20of%20the%20relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20cooperation%20between%20India%20and%20Bhutan%20in%20the%20hydro-power%20sector%20is%20covered%20under%20the%202006%20bilateral%20agreement%20for%20cooperation%20and%20its%20Protocol%20signed%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pact%20and%20the%20protocol%20were%20inked%20during%20Dr%20Singh's%20tenure%20as%20the%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735391820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fsq9plka_manmohan-singh-bhutan-special-prayer_625x300_28_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbhutan-holds-special-prayers-for-manmohan-singh-king-attends-funeral-7351372%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bhutan's%20King%20Jigme%20Khesar%20Namgyel%20Wangchuck%20on%20Saturday%20attended%20the%20funeral%20of%20former%20prime%20minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20a%20day%20after%20leading%20the%20Himalayan%20nation%20in%20offering%20prayers%20for%20the%20Indian%20leader%20at%20a%20Buddhist%20monastery%20in%20Thimphu.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbhutan-holds-special-prayers-for-manmohan-singh-king-attends-funeral-7351372%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Azerbaijan%20plane%20crash%3A%20Putin%20apologises%20for%20'tragic%20incident'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735391580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116744031%2Cimgsize-559984.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Frussian-air-defence-active-when-plane-crashed-russian-president-putin-to-azerbaijan-counterpart-ilham-aliyev%2Farticleshow%2F116744006.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Frussian-air-defence-active-when-plane-crashed-russ