3B%20to%20help%20employees%20experiment%20with%20generative%20AI%20tools.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20firm's%20chief%20learning%20officer%20said%20employees%20needed%20a%20safe%2C%20low-stakes%20format%20to%20experiment%20with%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPwC%20announced%20last%20year%20it%20was%20investing%20%241%20billion%20over%20three%20years%20to%20expand%20its%20AI%20capabilities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-wall-street-using-ai-generative-artificial-intelligence-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGenerative%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20reshaping%20the%20workplace%2C%20but%20many%20employees%20are%20still%20unsure%20how%20to%20use%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPwC%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalary-of-consultants-accountants-big-4-deloitte-kpmg-ey-pwc-2020-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBig%20Four%3C%2Fa%3E%20professional%20services%20firm%2C%20is%20addressing%20that%20gap%20with%20%26quot%3Bprompting%20parties.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-four-deloitte-pwc-kpmg-ey-staff-revenues-focus-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPwC%3C%2Fa%3E%20announced%20it%20was%20investing%20%241%20billion%20over%20three%20years%20to%20expand%20its%20AI%20capabilities.%20Later%20that%20year%20the%20company%20launched%20My%20AI%2C%20an%20upskilling%20initiative%20for%20employees%20to%20get%20trained%20on%20how%20to%20use%20AI%20responsibly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Leah%20Houde%2C%20the%20chief%20learning%20officer%20at%20PwC%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20after%20the%20initial%20AI%20trainings%2C%20there%20was%20still%20a%20skill%20gap%20when%20it%20came%20to%20employees%20actually%20putting%20the%20technology%20to%20use%2C%20even%20though%20employees%20wanted%20to%20know%20more%20about%20how%20to%20use%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20AI%20was%20among%20the%20top%20five%20terms%20searched%20in%20PwC's%20internal%20learning%20and%20development%20platform%2C%20compared%20to%20being%20in%20the%20top%2015%20in%202023%20and%20not%20even%20in%20the%20top%20100%20in%202022%2C%20PwC%20represenatives%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cognitive%20load%20that%20it%20takes%20to%20just%20try%20something%20new%20in%20the%20course%20of%20doing%20what%20you're%20normally%20doing%20is%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20Houde%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20many%20employees%20just%20didn't%20know%20where%20to%20start%20with%20AI%20prompts%2C%20which%20are%20the%20written%20instructions%20given%20to%20an%20AI%20tool%20in%20order%20to%20elicit%20a%20useful%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20needed%20a%20safe%2C%20low-stakes%20place%20to%20play%20with%20the%20tools.%20That's%20where%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprompt-engineer-ai-careers-tech-fad-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20prompting%3C%2Fa%3E%20parties%20came%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20sessions%2C%20which%20can%20be%20run%20independently%20amongst%20teams%20or%20by%20a%20company%20AI%20leader%2C%20are%20aimed%20at%20making%20employees%20comfortable%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-notetaker-work-meetings-tech-save-time-boost-efficiency-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20Microsoft%20Copilot%20and%20ChatPwC%20%E2%80%94%20the%20company's%20internal%20version%20of%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sessions%20focus%20on%20real%20use%20cases%2C%20so%20employees%20can%20collaboratively%20experiment%20with%20using%20AI%20to%20help%20them%20solve%20a%20problem%20or%20accomplish%20a%20task%20that's%20specific%20to%20their%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoude%20said%20the%20sessions%20are%20like%20a%C2%A0%26quot%3Bplayground%20where%20I'm%20not%20working%20on%20a%20client%20deliverable%20or%20writing%20an%20email%20to%20my%20boss%20or%20something%20that%20might%20give%20me%20anxiety%20that%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20mess%20up%20with%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20experimenting%20in%20a%20group%20setting%20also%20allows%20employees%20to%20learn%20from%20each%20others'%20prompts%2C%20giving%20them%20new%20ideas%20about%20what%20AI%20can%20do.%20It's%20also%20made%20them%20more%20likely%20to%20try%20out%20AI%20on%20their%20own%20time%20too%2C%20Houde%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20launching%20in%20March%2C%20PwC%20said%20it%20has%20hosted%20nearly%20500%20prompting%20parties%20and%20over%20880%20more%20have%20been%20requested%2C%20so%20they%20are%20scaling%20up%20to%20meet%20the%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoude%20said%20becoming%20familiar%20with%20AI%20was%20especially%20important%20for%20employees%20at%20PwC%20as%20a%20professional%20services%20firm%2C%20since%20the%20company's%20clients%20often%20turn%20to%20its%20employees%20to%20get%20their%20own%20questions%20about%20AI%20answered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkforce%20experts%20previously%20told%20BI's%20Tim%20Paradis%C2%A0that%20getting%20employees%20up%20to%20speed%20with%20AI%20is%20necessary%2C%20and%20that%20it%20will%20require%20the%20help%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-will-change-most-jobs-employers-help-workers-keep-up-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestment%20of%20employers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20survey%20published%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fslack.com%2Fintl%2Fen-gb%2Fblog%2Fnews%2Fthe-fall-2024-workforce-index-shows-ai-hype-is-cooling%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESlack%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20November%20found%20the%20rate%20of%20AI%20adoption%20among%20desk%20workers%20had%20plateaued%2C%20despite%20companies%20continuing%20to%20invest%20heavily%20in%20AI%20for%20their%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Houde%20said%20it's%20not%20just%20AI%20or%20other%20technical%20skills%20that%20employees%20at%20PwC%20want%20more%20training%20on.%20Terms%20like%C2%A0%26quot%3Binclusion%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Binc