table%20projects%20include%20'The%20Romantics'%20and%20'Yo%20Yo%20Honey%20Singh%3A%20Famous%2C'%20adding%20depth%20to%20Indian%20cinema's%20narrative%20landscape.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Bharti%20Dubey%20and%20Milana%20Rao%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nitish%20Reddy%20Overheard%20Relatives%20Cursing%20His%20Dad%20-%20How%20India%20Got%20A%20Star%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENitish%20Reddy%20loves%20his%20tattoos%20like%20most%2021-year-olds%20do%2C%20and%20one%20on%20his%20ankle%20is%20a%20picture%20of%20%E2%80%98Achilles'%20Heel'.%20He%20considers%20it%20a%20reminder%20of%20all%20the%20difficulties%20that%20his%20family%20has%20endured%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%20to%20power%20his%20cricketing%20dream.%20For%20Reddy%2C%20becoming%20a%20cricketer%20was%20both%20a%20choice%20and%20a%20compulsion.%20He%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20for%20his%20parents%2C%20who%20gave%20their%20tears%20and%20sweat%20to%20fuel%20his%20India%20dream.%20The%20middle-class%20family%20gambled%20with%20its%20finances%20to%20allow%20Reddy%20soar%20high.%20The%20risks%20taken%20and%20losses%20suffered%20will%20not%20bother%20them%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGetting%20into%20the%20Indian%20team%20is%20a%20proud%20feeling%20but%20it%20is%20only%2050%20percent%20of%20the%20dream.%20It%20will%20be%20fulfilled%20if%20I%20can%20wear%20that%20jersey%20and%20win%20matches%20for%20my%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20emotional%20Reddy%20had%20told%20PTI%20in%20June%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20see%20respect%20for%20my%20father%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20those%20who%20once%20tore%20him%20to%20shreds%20for%20believing%20in%20my%20talent.%26quot%3B%20The%20maiden%20Test%20ton%20celebration%20in%20Amarendra%20Bahubali%20style%20was%20a%20tribute%20to%20his%20father%20Mutyala%2C%20who%20watched%20his%20son%20rescue%20India%20from%20the%20stand%20behind%20team's%20dug-out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20was%20not%20just%20Reddy's%20but%20also%20of%20his%20father's%20sacrifices%20and%20belief%20that%20his%20son%20was%20special.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%2012%20year-old%2C%20Reddy%20overheard%20his%20relatives%20cursing%20his%20father%20for%20losing%20money%20in%20his%20micro-financing%20business%20after%20taking%20a%20voluntary%20retirement%20from%20service%20(VRS)%20from%20Hindustan%20Zinc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20took%20the%20decision%20to%20avoid%20getting%20transferred%20to%20Udaipur%20since%20he%20knew%20the%20city%20did%20not%20have%20the%20facilities%20and%20coaching%20to%20help%20his%20son%20excel%20as%20a%20cricketer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20invested%20the%20payout%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20to%20start%20his%20business.%20However%2C%20his%20friends%2C%20who%20took%20loan%20from%20him%20never%20returned%20the%20amount%2C%20resulting%20in%20massive%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20could%20hear%20those%20discussions%20and%20even%20as%20a%2012-year%20old.%20I%20understood%20everything.%20It%20was%20a%20promise%20I%20made%20to%20myself%20that%20only%20one%20thing%20can%20redeem%20my%20dad's%20prestige%20%E2%80%94%20an%20India%20call-up%2C%26quot%3B%20Reddy%20had%20told%20back%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20time%20when%20he%20could%20just%20afford%20one%20bat%20a%20year%20(one%20good%20seasoned%20English%20willow%20cost%20around%2015%2C000%20back%20then.%20It%20is%20close%20to%2050k%20now%20for%20international%20players).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20tell%20you%20how%20happy%20I%20am%2C%26quot%3B%20Mutyala%20said%2C%20struggling%20to%20express%20his%20emotions%2C%20standing%20outside%20the%20MCG%20after%20his%20son's%20recuse%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVirat%20sir%20has%20told%20him%20to%20work%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20back%2C%20Reddy%20was%20adjudged%20the%20best%20U-16%20cricketer%20by%20the%20BCCI%20and%20he%20attended%20the%20Annual%20Awards%20Function%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20Indian%20team%20was%20in%20attendance%20and%20the%2014-year-old%20was%20desperate%20for%20a%20selfie%20with%20Kohli%20and%20his%20wife%20Anushka%2C%20who%20were%20waiting%20near%20the%20elevator%20of%20the%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%20was%20in%20a%20hurry%20but%20obliged%20and%20it%20became%20a%20memorable%20moment%20for%20young%20Reddy.%20Now%20getting%20applauded%20for%20his%20effort%20by%20his%20idol%20is%20an%20unforgettable%20memory%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReddy's%20family%20also%20can't%20thank%20enough%20former%20Andhra%20Cricket%20Association's%20head%20MSK%20Prasad%20for%20enrolling%20him%20in%20its%20state-of-the-art%20academy%20in%20Visakhapatnam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInitially%2C%20he%20was%20placed%20in%20our%20U-14%20academy%2C%20located%20far%20from%20his%20hometown.%20However%2C%20his%20parents%20encouraged%20him%20to%20pursue%20his%20dreams%2C%20and%20he%20steadily%20progressed%20through%20our%20academies.%20Nitish%20eventually%20earned%20a%20spot%20in%20India's%20U-19%20team%2C%20showcasing%20his%20skill%20and%20determination%2C%26quot%3B%20Prasad%20recently%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Reddy%20secured%20spot%20in%20India's%20Emerging%20Asia%20Cup%20team%20but%20was%20dropped%20after%20playing%20a%20few%20games.%20The%20squad%20had%20players%20like%20Yash%20Dhull%2C%20Nishant%20Sindhu%2C%20who%20are%20far%20away%20from%20national%20reckoning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20certain%20events%20that%20change%20the%20course%20of%20one's%20career%20and%20that%20Emerging%20Asia%20Cup%20made%20him%20realise%20that%20to%20make%20a%20mark%20at%20the%20international%20level%2C%20he%20needed%20to%20think%20out%20of%20the%20box.%20%26quot%3BI%20started%20spending%20more%20time%20at%20the%20nets%20and%20also%20hired%20a%20few%20side%20arm%20specialists%20(throwdown)%20available%20in%20Vizag%20and%20practised%20for%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20all%20hurling%20the%20ball%20at%20145%20clicks%20and%20initially%20I%20found%20it%20hard.%20And%20then%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20month%20got%20adjusted.%20That%20practice%20went%20a%20long%20way%20when%20I%20played%20IPL%20this%20season%20where%20I%20could%20hit%20sixes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20SRH%20skipper%20Pat%20Cummins%20might%20be%20smiling%20quietly%20and%20thinking%20aloud%20as%20to%20why%20he%20told%20Reddy%20that%20he%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20play%20for%20India%20and%20develop%20into%20a%20good%20all-rounder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20head%20coach%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20also%20deserves%20credit%20for%20putting%20his%20foot%20down%20for%20having%20Reddy%20Down%20Under%20after%20watching%20his%20exploits%20in%20a%20T20%20series%20against%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%20and%20Reddy%20is%20now%20the%20'find%20of%20the%20series'%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Christmas%20Day%2C%20when%20everyone%20was%20fretting%20about%20India's%20combination%2C%20Sanjay%20Manjrekar%20had%20questioned%2C%20%26quot%3BWill%20Leaving%20Reddy%20out%20give%20India%20a%20better%20balance%3F%26quot%3B%20On%20Saturday%2C%20one%20of%20Reddy's%20sponsors%2C%20a%20popular%20sports%20equipment%20and%20apparel%20brand%20quote%20tweeted%20Manjrekar%20with%20the%20cricketer's%20pic%20urged%20the%20cricket%20pundit%20to%20keep%20quiet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735389060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fol830d5_nitish-reddy_625x300_28_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fnitish-reddy-the-story-of-sacrifices-made-by-a-middle-class-family-7350238%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nitish%20Reddy's%20j