e's%20a%20look%20at%20Nicole%20Kidman's%20best%20and%20worst%20movies%2C%20according%20to%20critics%20on%20Rotten%20Tomatoes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jguerrasio%40insider.com%20(Jason%20Guerrasio)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnicole-kidman-best-worst-movies%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lt%20Governor%20Orders%20Probe%20Into%20AAP's%20Schemes%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Poses%20Question%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Lt%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%20today%20ordered%20investigations%20into%20allegations%20concerning%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party's%20schemes%20ahead%20of%20the%20assembly%20elections%20scheduled%20for%20next%20year.%20The%20Lt%20Governor's%20office%20has%20issued%20separate%20directives%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Secretary%20and%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%2C%20based%20on%20complaints%20raised%20by%20Congress%20leader%20Sandeep%20Dikshit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20chief%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20termed%20the%20allegations%20against%20his%20party%20as%20%26quot%3Bfake%26quot%3B%20and%20posed%20a%20question%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat%20will%20they%20investigate%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20include%20claims%20about%20fraudulent%20collection%20of%20personal%20data%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20AAP's%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana%2C%20the%20presence%20of%20Punjab%20intelligence%20officers%20near%20the%20residences%20of%20Congress%20candidates%2C%20and%20the%20alleged%20transfer%20of%20cash%20from%20Punjab%20to%20Delhi%20to%20influence%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dikshit's%20complaint%20also%20flagged%20concerns%20about%20the%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana%2C%20an%20AAP%20initiative%20promising%20a%20monthly%20payment%20of%20Rs%202%2C100%20to%20eligible%20women.%20The%20LG%20has%20ordered%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20to%20conduct%20an%20inquiry%20through%20the%20Divisional%20Commissioner%20into%20the%20alleged%20collection%20of%20personal%20data%20by%20private%20individuals%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20enrolling%20beneficiaries.%20The%20Delhi%20Police%20has%20been%20instructed%20to%20take%20legal%20action%20against%20those%20breaching%20citizens'%20privacy%20by%20organising%20unauthorised%20registration%20camps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20repeatedly%20asking%20what%20would%20the%20BJP%20do%20by%20contesting%20elections.%20What%20is%20their%20plan%3F%20Today%20we%20got%20to%20know%20that%20if%20they%20win%2C%20they%20will%20stop%20the%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana%2C%20Sanjeevani%20Yojana%2C%20free%20electricity%2C%20free%20education%20and%20free%20electricity%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20government's%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20and%20Health%20departments%20had%20earlier%20issued%20public%20notices%20stating%20that%20the%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana%20and%20the%20Sanjeevani%20Yojana%20lacked%20government%20approval%20and%20were%20%26quot%3Bnon-existent.%26quot%3B%20These%20notices%20warned%20citizens%20against%20sharing%20personal%20details%20with%20unauthorised%20individuals%20and%20described%20the%20registrations%20as%20fraudulent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20said%20that%20after%20winning%20the%20election%2C%20we%20would%20give%20Rs%202%2C100%20to%20women%20and%20free%20treatment%20to%20the%20elderly%20above%2060%20years%20of%20age.%20Both%20these%20schemes%20were%20so%20beneficial%20for%20the%20public%20that%20lakhs%20of%20people%20registered%20for%20them%20already.%20This%20made%20the%20BJP%20nervous%2C%20many%20BJP%20leaders%20told%20me%20that%20to%20forget%20about%20winning%2C%20the%20BJP's%20deposit%20would%20be%20forfeited%20in%20many%20places%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said.%C2%A0%26quot%3BFirst%2C%20they%20sent%20their%20goons%2C%20then%20sent%20the%20police%20and%20uprooted%20the%20registration%20camp%2C%20today%20they%20have%20ordered%20a%20fake%20investigation%20that%20there%20will%20be%20an%20investigation.%20What%20will%20they%20investigate%3F%20We%20had%20made%20an%20election%20announcement%20that%20if%20we%20win%20the%20election%2C%20we%20will%20implement%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dikshit's%20complaint%20to%20the%20Lt%20Governor%20claimed%20cash%20being%20transported%20from%20Punjab%20to%20Delhi%2C%20allegedly%20to%20fund%20election-related%20activities.%20The%20LG's%20office%20has%20directed%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20Commissioner%20to%20monitor%20vehicles%20entering%20the%20city%20from%20neighbouring%20states.%20Police%20forces%20in%20neighbouring%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20and%20Rajasthan%20have%20also%20been%20alerted%20to%20prevent%20any%20potential%20illegal%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20serious%20allegation%2C%20Mr%20Dikshit%20claimed%20that%20Punjab%20intelligence%20officers%20were%20stationed%20near%20Congress%20candidates'%20residences%20in%20Delhi.%20The%20LG's%20office%20has%20directed%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20Commissioner%20to%20investigate%20this%20claim%20and%20submit%20a%20detailed%20report%20within%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20shot%20back%2C%20accusing%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20of%20settling%20illegal%20immigrants%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20for%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20his%20party's%20government%20are%20continuously%20settling%20illegal%20voters%20in%20Delhi.%20Today%20we%20showed%206%20examples...Arvind%20Kejriwal%20does%20the%20work%20of%20settling%20illegal%20voters%20in%20Delhi%20before%20every%20assembly%20election.%20In%202015%2C%2014%20lakh%20votes%20were%20increased%2C%20in%202019%2C%209%20lakh%20votes%20were%20increased%20and%20the%20same%20conspiracy%20is%20being%20hatched%20in%20Delhi%20now%20but%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20will%20not%20let%20this%20conspiracy%20succeed.%20We%20have%20complained%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20we%20will%20do%20it%20today%20also%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Delhi%20B