ical%20experts%20are%20watching.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20strong%20back-to-back%20years%20for%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20investors%20are%20fixated%20on%20whether%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2F2025-stock-market-investment-outlooks-wall-street-prediction-roundup-sp500-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20bull%20rally%20will%20extend%20into%202025.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20a%20better%20idea%20of%20what%20investors%20should%20be%20watching%20next%20year%2C%20Business%20Insider%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20top%20technical%20experts%20on%20Wall%20Street%20and%20asked%20them%3A%20What%20is%20the%20most%20important%20stock%20market%20chart%20heading%20into%202025%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20interest%20rates%20to%20software%20stocks%2C%20here's%20what%20they're%20watching.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWill%20Tamplin%2C%20Fairlead%20Strategies%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22826%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20long%20term%20chart%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676f03ccbec2d3fdefeb3a22%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22625%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWill%20Tamplin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20December%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20Index%20(SPX)%20nearly%20met%20a%20measured%20move%20projection%20of%206118%2C%20which%20was%20targeted%20by%20a%20breakout%20in%20Q1%20of%20this%20year.%20The%20measured%20move%20projects%20the%20uptrend%20from%202020-2021%20off%20the%202022%20low.%20This%20indicates%20that%20a%20prolonged%20period%20of%20consolidation%20is%20likely%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%202025.%20The%20monthly%20MACD%20histogram%20suggests%20that%20momentum%20behind%20the%20uptrend%20has%20started%20to%20wane%20in%20Q4%2C%20further%20supporting%20corrective%20price%20action%20to%20start%202025%2C%26quot%3B%20Will%20Tamplin%2C%20senior%20analyst%20at%20Fairlead%20Strategies%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERyan%20Detrick%2C%20Carson%20Group%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221435%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20chart%20of%20bull%20market%20stock%20rallies%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676f035ebec2d3fdefeb3a08%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221157%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERyan%20Detrick%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBull%20markets%20are%20like%20cruise%20ships%3A%20once%20they%20get%20moving%2C%20they%20can%20be%20hard%20to%20stop.%20Going%20back%2050%20years%2C%20once%20a%20bull%20market%20made%20it%20into%20the%20third%20year%2C%20history%20said%20there%20could%20be%20a%20lot%20more%20left.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20five%20most%20recent%20bull%20markets%20that%20made%20it%20this%20far%20lasted%20at%20least%20until%20their%20fifth%20birthday%2C%20with%20an%20average%20gain%20of%20eight%20years%2C%20so%20don't%20give%20up%20on%20the%20bull%20just%20yet%20in%202025%2C%26quot%3B%20Ryan%20Detrick%2C%20the%20chief%20market%20strategist%20at%20Carson%20Group%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECraig%20Johnson%2C%20Piper%20Sandler%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221155%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20chart%20of%20the%2010%20year%20US%20Treasury%20yield%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676f032abec2d3fdefeb39f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22557%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECraig%20Johnson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%2010-year%20UST%20yield%20has%20reversed%20a%20long-term%20secular%20downtrend%20off%20the%201981%20highs.%20The%20higher%20high%20above%203.25%20('18%20highs)%20also%20validates%20the%20multi-decade%20reversal.%20Historically%2C%20post%20uptrend%20or%20downtrend%20reversals%2C%20a%20retest%20typically%20occurs%2C%26quot%3B%20Craig%20Johnson%2C%20chief%20market%20technician%20at%20Piper%20Sandler%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20suspect%20this%20retrace%2Fpull%20back%20to%20prior%20resistance%20to%20find%20support%20around%203.00%25%20-%203.50%25%202H2025.%20A%20decisive%20break%20below%20that%20level%20would%20suggest%20the%20economy%20is%20in%20serious%20trouble.%20Until%20then%2C%20don't%20forget%20that%20slow%20and%20moderate%20Fed%20rate%20cuts%20have%20historically%20been%20bullish%20for%20equities%2C%20especially%20for%20Small%20and%20Mid-Cap%20stocks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAri%20Wald%2C%20Oppenheimer%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22653%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20chart%20of%20momentum%20stock%20performance%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676f022a9de00e389eb39bf8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22434%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAri%20Wald%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20important%20chart%20we're%20watching%20heading%20into%202025%20is%20the%20performance%20of%20high-momentum%20stocks%20vs.%20low-momentum%20stocks%2C%20loosely%20defined%20as%20the%20top%20winners%20vs.%20top%20losers%20over%20a%20prior%2012-month%20basis.%20We%20recently%20reported%20that%20the%20momentum%20factor%20has%20historically%20outperformed%20in%20the%20period%20between%20the%20cycle's%20broadest%20moment%2C%20when%20the%20most%20stocks%20are%20participating%2C%20and%20the%20market's%20final%20peak.%20Looking%20ahead%2C%20we%20see%20two%20potential%20scenarios%3A%201)%20the%20bull%20cycle%20broadens%20further%20driven%20by%20%26quot%3Bcatch-up%26quot%3B%20into%20low-momentum%20(losers)%3B%20this%20would%20be%20a%20bullish%20scenario%20for%20all%20stocks.%20Or%2C%202)%20the%20bull%20cycle%20narrows%20weighed%20down%20by%20low-momentum%2C%20and%20the%20MO%20factor%20continues%20to%20outperform%2C%26quot%3B%20Ari%20Wald%2C%20managing%20director%20at%20Oppenheimer%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJay%20Woods%2C%20Freedom%20Capital%20Markets%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221251%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20technical%20chart%20of%20software%20stocks%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676f01b0a3e82c79120495d2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22659%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStockcharts.com%2C%20Jay%20Woods%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B2025%20is%20the%20show-me%20year%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20technology.%20Investors%20want%20results%2C%20and%20software%20stocks%20are%20ready%20to%20lead%20that%20charge.%20Technically%2C%20we%20experienced%20a%20beta%20full-rounded%20bottom%20base%20over%20a%20two-year%20stretch%20in%202022-23.%20It%20broke%20out%20in%202024%20but%20spent%20most%20of%20that%20time%20consolidating%20slightly%20higher%20before%20finally%20making%20its%20upward%20move%20in%20late%202024%20with%20a%20beautiful%20upside%20gap%20(circled)%20in%20October%2C%26quot%3B%20Jay%20Woods%2C%20chief%20market%20strategist%20at%20Freedom%20Capital%20Markets%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThat%20gap%20can%20be%20used%20as%20a%20perfect%20risk%2Freward%20set-up.%20If%20there%20is%20further%20weakness%20into%202025%20that%2095%20level%20should%20be%20the%20downside%20risk%20area%20to%20watch.%20The%20upside%20targets%20seem%20much%20more%20likely%2C%20making%20this%20a%20sector%20and%20trade%20to%20watch%20for%202025.%20Look%20for%20the%20sector%20to%20not%20only%20eclipse%20its%20recent%20all-time%20highs%20but%20to%20add%20to%20them%20by%20some%2020%25.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDavid%20Keller%2C%20Sierra%20Alpha%20Research%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stock%20market%20chart%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676f0105a3e82c79120495b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStockcharts.com%2C%20David%20Keller%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%