quot%3BI%20think%20at%20that%20stage%2C%20why%20do%20you%20need%20to%20take%20a%20run%20that%20carries%20an%20element%20of%20risk%3F%20You're%20batting%20well%2C%20runs%20are%20coming.%20At%20that%20stage%2C%20the%20risk%20was%20not%20really%20necessary.%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%2C%20however%2C%20added%20that%20Kohli%20could%20have%20completed%20the%20run%20if%20had%20fully%20committed%20himself%20to%20it%20%26quot%3Bonly%20because%20Kohli%20is%20such%20a%20fantastic%20runner%26quot%3B%20between%20the%20wickets.%20The%20horrible%20mix-up%20led%20to%20Jaiswal's%20run%20out%20and%20affected%20Kohli's%20concentration%2C%20who%20then%20fished%20at%20a%20delivery%20outside%20off-stump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELanger%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20risky%20run%20because%20Pat%20Cummins%20is%20a%20brilliant%20athlete.%20Even%20if%20he%20hadn't%20picked%20it%20up%2C%20in%20the%20head%20of%20Pat%20Cummins%2C%20he%20would%20have%20gone%20for%20the%20non-striker.%20It%20would%20have%20been%20close%2C%20but%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20risky%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20that%20stage%20of%20the%20game%2C%20there%20was%20no%20need%20for%20it.%20They%20were%20on%20top.%20They%20had%20it%20absolutely%20under%20control.%20As%20fast%20as%20he%20is%2C%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20too%20risky%20a%20run%20to%20take.%20I%20love%20seeing%20guys%20drop%20and%20run%20hard%2C%20but%20that%20was%20a%20risky%20run.%20I%20think%20that's%20what%20Virat%20was%20saying.%26quot%3B%20A%20familiar%20collapse%20unfolded%20after%20Jaiswal's%20exit%20as%20India%20stumbled%20to%20164%2F5.%20The%20visitors%20trail%20by%20310%20after%20the%20hosts%20posted%20474%20all%20out%20in%20their%20first%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGavaskar%20said%20India%20need%20to%20put%20their%20%26quot%3Bhead%20down%26quot%3B%20and%20try%20and%20get%20as%20close%20as%20possible%20to%20Australia's%20total.%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20and%20Rishabh%20Pant%20were%20in%20the%20middle%20when%20stumps%20were%20ca