%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F116739376.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20United%20States'%20THAAD%20missile%20defense%20system%20was%20used%20in%20Israel%20for%20the%20first%20time%20to%20intercept%20a%20Houthi%20ballistic%20missile%20from%20Yemen.%20The%20interception's%20success%20is%20under%20analysis%2C%20with%20no%20confirmation%20if%20it%20was%20by%20the%20American%20or%20Israeli%20system.%20THAAD%20is%20designed%20to%20destroy%20missiles%20using%20hit-to-kill%20technology.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fwatch-israel-deploys-us-thaad-system-for-first-time-what-is-it%2Farticleshow%2F116739376.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fwatch-israel-deploys-us-thaad-system-for-first-time-what-is-it%2Famp_articleshow%2F116739376.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fwatch-israel-deploys-us-thaad-system-for-first-time-what-is-it%2Famp_articleshow%2F116739376.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22London%20Driver%20Sent%20Flowers%2C%20Bracelet%20To%20Qatari%20Princess.%20Then%20This%20Happened%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20London%20chauffeur%2C%20who%20believed%20he%20was%20in%20a%20romantic%20relationship%20with%20a%20Qatari%20princess%2C%20has%20been%20sentenced%20to%20a%2012-month%20community%20order%20and%20a%2030-day%20rehabilitation%20activity%20requirement%20by%20Westminster%20Magistrates'%20Court.%20Jihad%20Abousalah%2C%2047%2C%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20stalking%20Haya%20Al-Thani%2C%20a%20Qatari%20princess.%20The%20court%20was%20told%20that%20Abousalah%2C%20employed%20as%20Al-Thani's%20chauffeur%2C%20believed%20he%20was%20romantically%20involved%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProsecutor%20David%20Burns%20detailed%20how%20Abousalah's%20behaviour%20escalated%2C%20including%20sending%20Al-Thani%20gifts%20such%20as%20a%20bracelet%20and%20flowers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20notes%20wishing%20her%20a%20happy%20birthday.%20While%20Al-Thani%20was%20in%20Doha%2C%20she%20began%20receiving%20many%20phone%20calls%20from%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbousalah%20also%20visited%20Al-Thani's%20London%20residence%2C%20trying%20to%20send%20flowers%20to%20her%20through%20a%20member%20of%20her%20staff.%20His%20continuous%20behaviour%20raised%20significant%20concern%2C%20prompting%20Al-Thani%20to%20ask%20her%20husband%2C%20Mohamed%20Al-Thani%2C%20to%20arrange%20for%20private%20security%20to%20ensure%20her%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20heard%20that%20Al-Thani's%20daily%20life%20was%20severely%20disrupted%20by%20Abousalah's%20actions.%20She%20reported%20feeling%20unsafe%20in%20her%20own%20home%20and%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20Abousalah's%20knowledge%20of%20her%20children's%20schedules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prosecutor%2C%20David%20Burns%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CShe%20(Al-Thani)%20said%20the%20whole%20incident%20caused%20her%20alarm%20and%20distress.%20She%20has%20said%20she%20could%20not%20go%20about%20her%20normal%20day-to-day%20life.%20She%20feels%20she%20needs%20protection%20for%20herself%20and%20for%20her%20children.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20princess%20even%20frequently%20looked%20out%20of%20her%20windows%20to%20ensure%20he%20was%20not%20nearby%2C%20Burns%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefence%20counsel%20Sundeep%20Pankhania%20told%20the%20court%20that%20Abousalah's%20actions%20were%20influenced%20by%20mental%20illness.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20(Abousalah)%20had%20an%20ill-formed%20view%20that%20he%20was%20in%20a%20relationship%20with%20the%20princess.%20He%20divorced%20his%20wife%20because%20he%20genuinely%20held%20that%20belief.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Louisa%20Cieciora%20acknowledged%20the%20impact%20of%20Abousalah's%20mental%20health%20on%20his%20actions%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CYour%20responsibility%20is%20substantially%20reduced%20by%20reason%20of%20your%20mental%20disorder.%E2%80%9D%20But%20she%20also%20noted%20the%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20serious%20distress%E2%80%9D%20caused%20to%20Al-Thani%20and%20her%20family.%20Recognising%20his%20remorse%2C%20Cieciora%20sentenced%20Abousalah%20to%20a%20community%20order%20and%20mandated%20participation%20in%20rehabilitation%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20three-year%20restraining%20order%20was%20issued%2C%20prohibiting%20Abousalah%20from%20contacting%20Al-Thani%20or%20her%20husband%20and%20barring%20him%20from%20London's%20Hyde%20Park%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735380780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-02%2F65u9rvc8_london-police-generic_650x400_02_February_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchauffeur-s-delusion-leads-to-stalking-qatari-royal-court-imposes-restraining-order-7349957%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20London%20chauffeur%2C%20who%20believed%20he%20was%20in%20a%20romantic%20relationship%20with%20a%20Qatari%20princess%2C%20has%20been%20sentenced%20to%20a%2012-month%20community%20order%20and%20a%2030-day%20rehabilitation%20activity%20requirement%20by%20Westminster%20Magistrates'%20Court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchauffeur-s-delusion-leads-to-stalking-qatari-royal-court-imposes-restraining-order-7349957%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Deepika%20prioritizes%20raising%20daughter%20Dua%20over%20work%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735380749000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116739451%2Cimgsize-765084.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftelugu%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fdeepika-padukone-prioritizing-raising-daughter-dua-over-work-kalki-2898-ad-to-be-delayed%2