%20human%20extinction%20in%20the%20next%2030%20years.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnProf%20Hinton%2C%20awarded%20the%20Nobel%20Prize%20in%20Physics%20earlier%20this%20year%20for%20his%20work%20in%20the%20field%2C%20estimates%20a%20%E2%80%9C10%25%20to%2020%25%E2%80%9D%20chance%20that%20AI%20could%20result%20in%20human%20extinction%20over%20the%20next%20three%20decades.%20This%20is%20an%20increase%20from%20his%20earlier%20prediction%20of%20a%2010%25%20likelihood.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20an%20interview%20with%20BBC%20Radio%204's%20Today%20programme%2C%20Mr%20Hinton%20was%20asked%20whether%20his%20views%20on%20a%20potential%20AI%20apocalypse%20had%20changed.%20He%20responded%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CNot%20really%2C%2010%25%20to%2020%25.%E2%80%9D%20When%20asked%20if%20the%20odds%20had%20increased%2C%20Hinton%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20anything.%20You%20see%2C%20we've%20never%20had%20to%20deal%20with%20things%20more%20intelligent%20than%20ourselves%20before.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHe%20added%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20how%20many%20examples%20do%20you%20know%20of%20a%20more%20intelligent%20thing%20being%20controlled%20by%20a%20less%20intelligent%20thing%3F%20There%20are%20very%20few%20examples.%20There's%20a%20mother%20and%20baby.%20Evolution%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20into%20allowing%20the%20baby%20to%20control%20the%20mother%2C%20but%20that's%20about%20the%20only%20example%20I%20know%20of.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMr%20Hinton%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20professor%20emeritus%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Toronto%2C%20described%20humans%20as%20toddlers%20when%20compared%20to%20advanced%20AI%20systems.%20%E2%80%9CI%20like%20to%20think%20of%20it%20as%3A%20imagine%20yourself%20and%20a%20three-year-old.%20We'll%20be%20three-year-olds%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHis%20concerns%20regarding%20the%20technology%20first%20became%20publicly%20known%20when%20he%20resigned%20from%20his%20role%20at%20Google%20in%202023%20to%20speak%20more%20freely%20about%20the%20dangers%20of%20unregulated%20AI%20development.%20He%20warned%20that%20%E2%80%9Cbad%20actors%E2%80%9D%20could%20exploit%20AI%20to%20cause%20harm.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnReflecting%20on%20the%20rapid%20progress%20of%20AI%20development%2C%20Hinton%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20didn't%20think%20it%20would%20be%20where%20we%20(are)%20now.%20I%20thought%20at%20some%20point%20in%20the%20future%20we%20would%20get%20here.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHe%20expressed%20concern%20that%20experts%20in%20the%20field%20now%20predict%20AI%20systems%20could%20become%20smarter%20than%20humans%20in%20the%20next%2020%20years%2C%20saying%20it's%20%E2%80%9Ca%20very%20scary%20thought.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMr%20Hinton%20underscored%20the%20need%20for%20government%20regulation%2C%20noting%20the%20pace%20of%20development%20was%20%E2%80%9Cvery%2C%20very%20fast%2C%20much%20faster%20than%20I%20expected.%E2%80%9D%20He%20warned%20that%20relying%20only%20on%20big%20companies%20driven%20by%20profit%20motives%20would%20not%20ensure%20the%20safe%20development%20of%20AI.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20thing%20that%20can%20force%20those%20big%20companies%20to%20do%20more%20research%20on%20safety%20is%20government%20regulation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735372860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F66q6se98_geoffrey-hinton_625x300_08_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgeoffrey-hinton-godfather-of-ai-warns-technology-could-wipe-out-humanity-7349511%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Geoffrey%20Hinton%2C%20awarded%20the%20Nobel%20Prize%20in%20Physics%2C%20has%20raised%20concerns%20that%20the%20technology%20may%20lead%20to%20human%20extinction%20in%20the%20next%2030%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgeoffrey-hinton-godfather-of-ai-warns-technology-could-wipe-out-humanity-7349511%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22