a-emas_11zon-1734669896.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Senior%20citizens%20deserve%20to%20enjoy%20their%20final%20innings%20without%20financial%20worries%20and%20medical%20hassles.%5C%22%20data-id%3D%5C%22391137%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fwarga-emas_11zon-1734669896.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fwarga-emas_11zon-1734669896-300x188.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fwarga-emas_11zon-1734669896-500x313.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fwarga-emas_11zon-1734669896-768x480.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fwarga-emas_11zon-1734669896-150x94.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-391137%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESenior%20citizens%20deserve%20to%20enjoy%20their%20final%20innings%20without%20financial%20worries%20and%20medical%20hassles.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20particularly%20crucial%20for%20those%20managing%20pre-existing%20conditions%20like%20diabetes%20or%20hypertension%2C%20which%20can%20significantly%20impact%20healthcare%20costs.%20Moreover%2C%20pre-existing%20illnesses%20can%20influence%20health%20insurance%20premiums%2C%20potentially%20resulting%20in%20higher%20costs%20or%20even%20denial%20of%20coverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20the%20Ayushman%20Vaya%20Vandana%20Card%20aims%20to%20change%20the%20lives%20of%20senior%20citizens%20in%20India%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComprehensive%20Coverage%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Cardholders%20can%20receive%20cashless%20treatment%20worth%20up%20to%20Rs%205%20lakh%20annually%20at%20empanelled%20hospitals%20across%20India%2C%20covering%20an%20extensive%20range%20of%20medical%20procedures.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%