%20ground%20are%20working%20towards%20that%20goal%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bihari%20Lal%20Banjara%20(48)%20of%20Bhilwara%2C%20Gangapur%2C%20who%20works%20closely%20with%20Paras%20shares%2C%20explaining%20how%20a%20lack%20of%20documentation%20could%20deny%20their%20children%20the%20basic%20right%20of%20education.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Paras%20established%20%E2%80%98Olakhaan%20Trust%E2%80%99%20where%20they%20work%20with%20around%2020%20villages.%20Through%20his%20work%20in%20the%20field%2C%20they%20have%20developed%20a%20network%20of%20people%20who%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F278791%2Fwomen-led-deepa-pawar-anubhuti-uplifts-nomadic-tribes-rights-mental-health%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eencourage%20the%20nomadic%20communities%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20proactive%20and%20help%20with%20documentation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20volunteers%20and%20workers%20who%20assist%20people%20while%20going%20to%20offices%20and%20helping%20them%20through%20the%20whole%20process%20of%20documentation.%20We%20are%20essentially%20a%20community%20organisation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Paras%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20working%20with%20other%20organisations%2C%20I%20realised%20they%20tackled%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20issues.%20However%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20fully%20focus%20on%20one%20cause.%20There%20aren%E2%80%99t%20any%20organisations%20that%20specifically%20work%20for%20nomads%2C%20and%20since%20identity%20is%20a%20crucial%20part%20of%20what%20I%20do%2C%20it%20made%20sense%20to%20carve%20out%20a%20distinct%20identity%20for%20this%20issue%2C%20separate%20from%20other%20concerns.%20I%20wanted%20to%20focus%20exclusively%20on%20this%2C%20working%20in%20smaller%20areas%20and%20regions%20to%20create%20a%20more%20targeted%20impact%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajmal%20Bhil%2C%20a%2032-year-old%20fellow%20at%20Olakhaan%20Trust%2C%20has%20assisted%20over%20200%20individuals%20in%20obtaining%20their%20caste%20certificates.%20%E2%80%9CI%20often%20give%20people%20rides%20to%20the%20panchayat%20office%20and%20fill%20their%20forms.%20We%20even%20managed%20to%20convince%20the%20local%20cyber%20shop%20owner%20to%20stay%20open%20during%20the%20night%2C%20so%20the%20community%20could%20get%20their%20documents%20ready%20without%20losing%20the%20day%E2%80%99s%20wages%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20arranging%20camps%20and%20with%20the%20support%20of%20their%20community%20members%2C%20Olakhaan%20has%20been%20able%20to%20help%20about%20400%20individuals%20from%20these%20communities%20procure%20caste%20certificates%2C%20and%20other%20government%20IDs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20Patta%20Abhiyan%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENomadic%20tribes%20make%20up%20about%208%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20yet%20one%20of%20the%20core%20challenges%20faced%20by%20the%20communities%20is%20the%20absence%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F239555%2Fmadhya-pradesh-woman-forest-tribal-adivasi-rights-activist-wins-award-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eland%20ownership%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Historically%2C%20nomads%20have%20lived%20in%20temporary%20settlements%2C%20often%20without%20any%20legal%20claim%20to%20the%20land%20they%20occupy.%20This%20has%20left%20them%20vulnerable%20to%20eviction%20by%20both%20government%20authorities%20and%20local%20villagers%2C%20who%20often%20carry%20some%20prejudice%20against%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20establishment%20of%20the%20Olakhaan%20Trust%2C%20Paras%20along%20with%20MKSS%20had%20helped%20launch%20the%20%E2%80%98Patta%20Abhiyan%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20campaign%20aimed%20at%20securing%20land%20rights%20for%20nomadic%20families%20as%20well.%20However%2C%20implementing%20this%20initiative%20has%20not%20been%20without%20its%20hurdles.%20Local%20panchayat%20authorities%20often%20resist%20granting%20land%20to%20nomads%20due%20to%20societal%20biases%2C%20and%20land%20allocation%20has%20been%20slow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202012%2C%20during%20the%20Jaipur%20%3Cem%3EJan%20Sunwai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Public%20Hearing)%2C%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20listened%20to%20the%20grievances%20of%20the%20nomadic%20communities.%20It%20was%20decided%20that%20these%20communities%2C%20who%20had%20been%20left%20without%20jobs%20or%20home%20security%2C%20would%20be%20classified%20under%20the%20Below%20Poverty%20Line%20(BPL)%20category.%20It%20was%20also%20announced%20that%20they%20would%20receive%20%E2%80%98patta%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20lands%20they%20had%20been%20living%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20official%20document%20would%20serve%20as%20proof%20of%20land%20ownership%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20finally%20have%20a%20place%20they%20could%20truly%20call%20home.%20The%20size%20of%20the%20patta%20would%20vary%3A%20450%20square%20feet%20for%20those%20living%20within%20or%20near%20a%20city%2C%20and%202%2C700%20square%20feet%20for%20those%20in%20rural%20villages.%20While%20many%20promises%20were%20made%20during%20this%20time%2C%20the%20implementation%20was%20uneven.%20Some%20promises%20were%20fulfilled%2C%20while%20others%20were%20only%20half-heartedly%20executed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mindset%20of%20people%20in%20the%20Panchayat%20offices%20was%20a%20significant%20obstacle%2C%20as%20many%20were%20reluctant%20to%20grant%20land%20to%20nomadic%20tribes%20due%20to%20prevailing%20stigma%20and%20stereotypes.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20low%20literacy%20rate%20meant%20having%20to%20help%20each%20member%20understand%20the%20process%20and%20even%20take%20them%20through%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20start%20by%20talking%20to%20people%2C%20asking%20if%20they%20needed%20help%20with%20their%20documentation.%20For%20those%20who%20did%2C%20we%20guided%20them%20through%20the%20process%20%E2%80%94%20telling%20them%20which%20office%20to%20visit%2C%20who%20to%20speak%20to%2C%20and%20how%20to%20write%20applications.%20If%20someone%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20write%20them%2C%20we%20would%20arrange%20for%20someone%20else%20to%20help%20with%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20Paras%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bhilwara%20district%20alone%2C%20because%20of%20the%20persistent%20efforts%20made%20by%20Paras%20and%20his%20team%2C%20about%201%2C000%20pattas%20were%20successfully%20allotted%2C%20although%20many%20across%20the%20state%20still%20remain%20without%20land.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20difficult%20to%20get%20ration%20without%20an%20address%20proof.%20We%20lived%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20the%20village%2C%20and%20when%20a%20road%20was%20built%20in%20front%20of%20our%20settlement%2C%20our%20land%20became%20more%20valuable%2C%20and%20people%20started%20trying%20to%20push%20us%20out.%20But%20thankfully%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Paras%20and%20Rajmal%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20stay%20and%20secure%20the%20documents%20for%20our%20450%20square%20feet%20of%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pappu%20Nath%20(40)%20is%20one%20of%20the%20recipients%20who%20recently%20received%20his%20land%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.24.51-AM-1734609106.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Paras%20holding%20a%20meeting%20with%20members%20of%20nomadic%20groups%20from%20his%20community%2C%20engaging%20in%20a%20discussion%20to%20address%20their%20issues%20and%20concerns.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.24.51-AM-1734609106.jpeg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-