20these%20kids%20as%20a%20scribe%2C%20and%20I%20realised%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20completely%20meritorious%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwalekhan%E2%80%99s%20aim%20was%20to%20eliminate%20the%20dependence%20on%20scribes%20during%20exams.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20visually%20impaired%20community%20has%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20strides%20in%20terms%20of%20becoming%20independent%2C%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20giving%20exams%2C%20they%20still%20depend%20on%20scribes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Uma%20says.%20Initially%2C%20they%20hoped%20the%20app%20would%20be%20widely%20adopted%20by%20older%20students%20in%20colleges%2C%20but%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20that%20the%20older%20students%20had%20become%20so%20dependent%20on%20scribes%20that%20they%20had%20acute%20anxiety%20on%20giving%20them%20on%20their%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20Uma%20reflects.%20So%2C%20they%20shifted%20focus%20to%20younger%20students.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201500px)%20100vw%2C%201500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FNiwantPune-143_11zon-1734329947.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20student%20using%20the%20app%20to%20type%20in%20Marathi%20independently%20without%20a%20scribe.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FNiwantPune-143_11zon-1734329947.jpg%201500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FNiwantPune-143_11zon-1734329947-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FNiwantPune-143_11zon-1734329947-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FNiwantPune-143_11zon-1734329947-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FNiwantPune-143_11zon-1734329947-1200x800.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetteri