a-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20route%20that%20trekkers%20use%20starts%20from%20Rimbik%2C%20or%20nearby%20Sirikhola%2C%20about%2055%20km%20from%20Darjeeling.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20due%20to%20the%20accessible%20motorable%20road%20we%20have%20nowadays%20that%20we%20choose%20the%20Rimbik%20route%2C%E2%80%9D%20Keshav%20Gurung%2C%20who%20runs%20the%20Shikhar%20Tarry%20homestay%20in%20Mane%20Bhanjyang%2C%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CGroups%20like%20%E2%80%98India%20Hikes%E2%80%99%20regularly%20use%20this%20route.%20They%20drive%20from%20here%20till%20Rimbik%20and%20then%20climb%20up%20from%20the%20other%20side%20through%20Phalut%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20to%20stay%20in%20Sandakphu%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%E2%80%99re%20planning%20a%20trip%20to%20Sandakphu%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20best%20to%20keep%20at%20least%20a%20week%20in%20hand.%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20Sandakphu%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20your%20choice%20whether%20you%20want%20to%20reach%20Phalut%20or%20climb%20down%20through%20Rimbik%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sasang%20says.%20The%20descent%20from%20the%20summit%20ends%20in%20the%20town%20of%20Rimbik%20and%20passes%20through%20Sirikhola.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhalut%2C%20the%20second-highest%20peak%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20remains%20a%20popular%20spot%20among%20trekkers%20due%20to%20its%20pristine%20location%2C%20breathtaking%20views%2C%20and%20colour%20tapestry%20created%20by%20full-bloom%20rhododendrons.%20Many%20believe%20that%20the%20trek%20to%20Sandakphu%20is%20incomplete%20without%20setting%20foot%20on%20Phalut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241201-WA0013-1735044127-500x667.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20sunset%20paints%20a%20silhouet