i%20Anantha%20has%20written%20four%20novels%20during%20the%20time%20she%20homeschooled%20and%20these%20are%20part%20of%20The%20JAZ%20Gang%20series.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20did%20you%20know%20it%20was%20time%20to%20homeschool%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20sit%20for%20hours%20in%20front%20of%20the%20screen%20for%20lectures.%20After%20class%2C%20we%20would%20be%20back%20again%20in%20front%20of%20the%20screen%20to%20complete%20our%20homework.%20It%20was%20stressful.%E2%80%9D%20Being%20an%20outdoor%20girl%20who%20loved%20sports%2C%20Vaishnavi%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20habituated%20to%20so%20much%20screen%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThings%20peaked%20after%20one%20particular%20Maths%20class%20when%2C%20after%20spending%20hours%20learning%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F270005%2Fmaths-in-indian-monuments-ancient-science-symmetry-architecture-heritage%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20geometry%20concept%20%3C%2Fa%3Eonline%2C%20Vaishnavi%20still%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20make%20head%20nor%20tail%20of%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20the%20day%20she%20told%20her%20parents%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20just%20can%E2%80%99t%20do%20it.%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20learning%20anything.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20homeschooling%20mean%20waking%20up%20late%20and%20doing%20what%20you%20please%3F%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20laughs%20Vaishnavi.%20She%20recalls%20her%20parents%E2%80%99%20firm%20instructions%C2%A0%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CYou%20need%20to%20utilise%20your%20time%20properly%2C%20follow%20a%20timetable%20and%20be