20the%20India%20of%20the%20past%2C%20people%E2%80%99s%20way%20of%20life%2C%20the%20food%20habits%20and%20the%20accommodation.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FFzpm4jWhF1g%3Fsi%3DsXQ-DWwHgiyzyL0M%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20homeschooling%20make%20you%20introverted%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidering%20you%20aren%E2%80%99t%20expected%20to%20dress%20up%20and%20go%20to%20school%2C%20participate%20in%20school%20events%2C%20have%20annual%20days%20or%20sports%20days%20to%20channel%20your%20energies%20in%2C%20there%20is%20an%20understandable%20tendency%20to%20retreat%20into%20a%20shell.%20But%20this%20is%20where%2C%20Vaishnavi%20says%2C%20your%20hobbies%20will%20play%20a%20role.%20%E2%80%9CWriting%20has%20helped%20me%20tremendously%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20skills%2C%20from%20designing%20the%20book%20cover%20to%20creating%20video%20trailers%20on%20my%20own.%20It%20has%20also%20forced%20me%20to%20come%20out%20of%20my%20introverted%20nature%20to%20promote%20my%20books%20on%20various%20platforms.%E2%80%9D%20She%20recalls%20participating%20in%20prestigious%20literary%20events%2C%20including%20three%20appearances%20at%20the%20National%20Hyderabad%20Book%20Fair%20and%20a%20chance%20to%20speak%20at%20the%20%E2%80%98Youngistan%20Nukkad%E2%80%99%20at%20the%20Hyderabad%20Literature%20Festival%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContending%20the%20assumption%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F262348%2Findia-homeschooling-tips-guidance-success-board-exams-marks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehomeschoolers%20%3C%2Fa%3Edon%E2%80%99t%20have%20friends%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20often%20think%20that%20homeschooling%20means%20an%20